title: Ghost Recon: Heroes Unleashed 1.0b8 Standalone [PC]
description:
TOM CLANCY'S GHOST RECON: HEROES UNLEASHED 1.0B8 STANDALONE (09/2012)

-standalone install (drag & drop) confirmed on WinXP/Vista/Win7/Win8 (x86/x64)
-DRM-free, no CD/SN required (just unzip and play)
-complete multiplayer support, LAN and online (direct IP, Xfire, GamerRanger)
-full Ghost Recon (v1.4) game incl. Desert Siege and Island Thunder expansions
-latest version of mega mod pack Ghost Recon: Heroes Unleashed (1.0b8 09/2012)
